First, create replication slot on primary 

SELECT pg_create_physical_replication_slot('for_claimpsprocess_03');

SELECT pg_create_physical_replication_slot('replica_slot');

Second, update the replication to use the slot!

primary_conninfo = 'host=primary_host port=5432 user=repl_user password=...'
primary_slot_name = 'for_claimprocess_03' -- Critical for WAL retention

